        - <span role="byline"></span>
    </section>

    <p>Aroma Truf­fle, known for its truf­fle chips, has two moon­cake op­tions: Black Char­coal Mu­sang King and But­ter­fly Pea Mu­sang King. In­fused with pre­mium Black Win­ter Truf­fles har­vested from Spo­leto, Italy, the moon­cakes com­bine the sweet and creamy yet mildly savoury and bit­ter durian (from Raub, Pa­hang) with a strong truf­fle aroma.</p>
    <p>WHERE: Aroma Truf­fle out­lets at Jewel Changi Air­port, Plaza Sin­ga­pura, Bugis+, Chi­na­town Point & West­gate MRT: Var­i­ous PRICE: $78 for a box of four (cus­tomers can choose four moon­cakes of the same flavour or two of each flavour)</p>
    <p>INFO: For on­line pur­chase, go to aro­ma­truf­fle.com</p>


